OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783698492
OL,3,CJersey Government to automatically
OL,4,Cshare personal data with credit firms
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey will begin
OL,7,Fautomatically sharing limited personal
OL,8,Fdata with some UK companies.
OL,10,FFrom Thursday 30 July, names,
OL,11,Faddresses, and dates of birth will be
OL,12,Fsecurely provided to the credit
OL,13,Freference agencies Experian and
OL,14,FEquifax to try and improve residents'
OL,15,Faccess to financial products such as
OL,16,Fcredit cards.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
