OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783698492
OL,3,CJersey Government to automatically
OL,4,Cshare personal data with credit firms
OL,6,FThe move comes after years of struggle
OL,7,Ffor Channel Islanders to access these
OL,8,Fservices, as some banks have declined
OL,9,Fapplications because they do not have
OL,10,Fa UK address.
OL,12,FRing-fencing laws introduced in 2019
OL,13,Fmean that UK finance firms are
OL,14,Frequired to keep their British and
OL,15,Foffshore operations separate.
OL,17,FThat meant that many credit card
OL,18,Fproviders could not access the central
OL,19,Fdatabase of personal information
OL,20,Fneeded to verify applications.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783698492
OL,3,CJersey Government to automatically
OL,4,Cshare personal data with credit firms
OL,6,FThe States of Jersey passed a law
OL,7,Fchange in 2023 that allowed the
OL,8,Fsharing of more information but
OL,9,Fproblems persisted. This latest tweak
OL,10,Fin policy will make the data available
OL,11,Fautomatically for the first time.
OL,13,FA similar process is already in place
OL,14,Fin the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
