CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783698492
OL,3,CJersey Government to automatically
OL,4,Cshare personal data with credit firms
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey who wish to opt out
OL,7,Fcan contact the Employment, Social
OL,8,FSecurity and Housing Department by
OL,9,Fcalling 01534 444444 (option 6) or
OL,10,Femailing customerservice@gov.je with
OL,11,Fthe subject header "OPT OUT", and
OL,12,Fincluding their full name, address and
OL,13,Fdate of birth.
OL,15,FHowever, the Government warns choosing
OL,16,Fnot to share this data may affect
OL,17,Fsomeone's ability to access financial
OL,18,Fproducts in the future.
OL,20,FKarl Walker, the Chairman of Jersey's
OL,21,FConsumer Council, welcomes the changes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783698492
OL,3,CJersey Government to automatically
OL,4,Cshare personal data with credit firms
OL,6,F"We're delighted," he said. "We're on
OL,7,Fthe brink of, once again, consumers
OL,8,Fbeing able to access a wider range of
OL,9,Fcredit card options."
OL,11,FAlthough the Government is taking
OL,12,Fsteps to simplify the process, it is
OL,13,Funclear whether any credit card
OL,14,Fproviders will look to rejoin the
OL,15,FJersey market.
OL,17,FMr Walker said that is "the elephant
OL,18,Fin the room" and hopes companies can
OL,19,Fbe persuaded to continue doing
OL,20,Fbusiness on the island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
