OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783698492
OL,3,CJersey Government to automatically
OL,4,Cshare personal data with credit firms
OL,6,FSocial Security Minister, Senator
OL,7,FElaine Millar, explained: "We've been
OL,8,Fworking in the background to address
OL,9,Fthis and we are now making a positive
OL,10,Fstep forward.
OL,12,F"Sharing our basic information will
OL,13,Fmake it easier for banks to carry out
OL,14,Fthe necessary checks and will give us
OL,15,Fmore choice and greater access to
OL,16,Fcredit cards in Jersey."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
